{"tid":1740113,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[一圖明解]美國點立一條法案","createTime":"2019-11-20T00:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T01:30:13.000Z","uid":198688,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec95f222c1a7e0f0ffe05a46e432bf691ddbe4b","tid":1740113,"uid":198688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vd5jmPz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVd5jmPz.png&h=6c8a4063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先恭喜過到Senate!<br />\n但因為法案有兩個ver.  所以睇圖就係step 4<br />\n但一整合到就會交俾侵侵，之後會有4個可能性<br />\n<br />\n1. 侵侵簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 法案生效<br />\n<br />\n2. 侵侵唔簽+退回法案俾參眾兩院，參眾兩院再投。只要贊成通過人數過三份二，就唔使侵侵簽名都立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 侵侵唔理法案擺響枱頭，既唔簽又唔退，10日後法案自動生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 侵侵10日內唔簽，退回法案俾國會，同時國會休會10日，法例先會自動失效"},{"pid":"18d06a541a23a6c630abf14e42932ad370c10b31","tid":1740113,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:09:51.000Z","msg":"Thanks 好清晰"},{"pid":"91bafe0c2ed2b951b9f75076297f75781c819276","tid":1740113,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預料明年</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCiQtqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCiQtqY.jpg&h=606d6185&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cebb3724e6ab895e6e43f6a9f63e6ae05415486c","tid":1740113,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"知道有好多條要排要等，可以插到隊已經好犀利<br />\n但係想問下第四種情況常唔常出現？ 有啲似無啦啦又拖死咗"},{"pid":"90fea212349ff4ad2e9cb61d7bb393422c656f06","tid":1740113,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"班兒登仔成日都話有2/3就唔洗侵簽<br />\n原來仲有pocket veto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872496a0c6f94c5a2d2c3c7d153954b4cd8d1802","tid":1740113,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cebb3724e6ab895e6e43f6a9f63e6ae05415486c","tid":1740113,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"知道有好多條要排要等，可以插到隊已經好犀利<br />\n但係想問下第四種情況常唔常出現？ 有啲似無啦啦又拖死咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"要有conference committee 先<br />\n因為兩個versions 唔同"},{"pid":"02bb5bcf4e1c32ace41128cf762529509a023871","tid":1740113,"uid":198688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18d06a541a23a6c630abf14e42932ad370c10b31","tid":1740113,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:09:51.000Z","msg":"Thanks 好清晰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:16:17.000Z","msg":"咁睇番d option<br />\n點樣先暫緩生效<br />\n只可以係侵侵10日內退番俾國會<br />\n國會唔過2/3贊成再彈番俾侵侵無限loop<br />\n但國會連Mitch都成功逼到宮要支持<br />\n好難轉軚帶埋其他黨員say no<br />\n所以2/3 贊成大家都可以安心<br />\n<br />\n而第四條令法案失效仲難<br />\n想國會休會除非中共出盡強力部門暗殺議員<br />\n但強力部門點夠CIA FBI鬥，除非個撚個葉問上身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18575f826d6137963b8e5fff0447b635f92c2846","tid":1740113,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8420b951b34d7552dd901c7c3bdbf426e04a2ff5","tid":1740113,"uid":198688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90fea212349ff4ad2e9cb61d7bb393422c656f06","tid":1740113,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"班兒登仔成日都話有2/3就唔洗侵簽<br />\n原來仲有pocket veto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB