ces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 美國唔係淨係pass香港人權法架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇都係入波大過唔入啦，而家成個波擺響12碼點，而家睇邊個做劊子手起腳既啫<br />\n維尼記住捉路睇住點撲喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}